title: Why haven't I received my Halloween Icons yet?
body: I defeated doom bots (several times now) and also gifted my friend, but I haven't received my icons. Any clue as to why?

replies.body: As *Zombiemaster* mentioned, it can take a while for them to be added to your account. If you don't have anything *after* November 17th has rolled around, please let me know!

The official [Teemoing website ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016) states that the icons can take up to 2 weeks after November 3rd to be added to your account. Just be patient and you will receive them soon enough.
